{"tid":986203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽見聲音要他襲擊　戰鬥民族闖紐約中餐廳鎚殺3中國人","createTime":"2019-01-18T09:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T10:10:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a73c3f30af2a78ea87ab3f6e1076d1f2b6ef5481","tid":986203,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"美國紐約布魯克林一名俄羅斯裔男子，周二（15日）進入一家中國人經營的自助海鮮餐廳，用鐵鎚攻擊店內的3名中國裔男子，造成1死2重傷。男子被捕後聲稱，聽見聲音要他襲擊陌生人。他還說，這些聲音到處都是，甚至在討論外星人。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，行兇的34歲男子馬湯諾維奇（Arthur Martunovich）當天先在餐廳入口大叫大喊，打傷一名員工後，走到餐廳後面，攻擊另一名員工。接著，馬湯諾維奇走進廚房，攻擊第3名被害者。餐廳內的客人見狀，嚇得趕緊逃命，有目擊顧客稱，看見一名員工被打到頭破血流，按著頭部走了幾步後倒地。警方透露，死者是來自中國福州亭江的34歲廚師潘富暉（Fufai Pun，音譯），傷者是60歲的餐廳老闆及50歲的經理。<br />\n<br />\n馬湯諾維奇後來在現場附近被捕，數名警員在制伏他時受傷。馬湯諾維奇目前被控謀殺和企圖謀殺等多項罪名，也被要求接受精神評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190118/1502844/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190118%2F1502844%2F&d=lH%2FTjTKhyl%2BMcbfhgwPB7zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=fb1c840b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190118%2F1502844%2F&h=843ae7c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190118/1502844/</a>"},{"pid":"d23db5d85aff3634de3451795de0ee457e14abba","tid":986203,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:26:52.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa0729a001ad0015c644e496d6bc506896178c7","tid":986203,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bbb88349d136062e55810f771fe1eedd70b046","tid":986203,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"只要凡是針對中國人，任何武力皆是正義"},{"pid":"5daa74df7afe4af3937ad9091aa704066a4897ee","tid":986203,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}